*September 22: {{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/christian-albums?chartDate=2007-09-22|title=Christian Albums (September 22, 2007)|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=June 18, 2012}}
