*October 9: {{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/catalog-albums?chartDate=2010-10-09|title=Catalog Albums (October 9, 2010)|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=June 17, 2012}}
